OL,8,Fdiscriminated against due to
OL,9,Fsuffering menopause symptoms will be
OL,10,Fheard by an employment tribunal this
OL,11,Fweek in a legal first.
OL,13,FThe Equality and Human Rights
OL,14,FCommission (EHCR), which is
OL,15,Fsupporting Maria Rooney's case, said
OL,16,Fshe was suffering from menopause
OL,17,Fsymptoms, anxiety and depression when
OL,18,Fshe took periods of extended sickness
OL,19,Fleave from her job as a social worker
OL,20,Ffor Leicester City Council in 2017
OL,21,Fand 2018.
